<p>Shortly after deployment, the Falcon 9 booster returned to Earth and landed on SpaceX's drone ship 'Of Course I Still Love You.'</p>

<p>The firm shared a tweet shortly after the mission regarding the satellites: 'In initial tests of Starlink, the team has been collecting latency data and performing standard speed tests of the system.'</p>

<p>'Results from these tests have shown super low latency and download speeds greater than 100 mbps – fast enough to stream multiple HD movies at once and still have bandwidth to spare.'</p>

